[log] bash[68] stdout   - `backup_path` (str): Path to the backup file (optional)
[log] bash[68] stdout   - `fuzzy_threshold` (float): Fuzzy matching threshold (optional)
[log] bash[68] stdout   - `max_results` (int): Maximum number of results (optional)
[log] bash[68] stdout   - `tab_entries_count` (int): Number of tab completion entries (optional)
[log] bash[68] stdout **Return Value**: A dictionary containing directory entry information (key=path, value=weight)
