[log] bash[68] stdout #### 21. _ActionsContainer
[log] bash[68] stdout **Function Description**:
[log] bash[68] stdout `_ActionsContainer` is a container class for managing and organizing command-line argument actions. It provides core functionalities such as adding, registering, and handling argument conflicts, serving as the foundation for `ArgumentParser`. It is responsible for storing argument actions, handling default values, and managing argument groups and mutually exclusive groups.
