[log] bash[68] stdout **Function Description**:
[log] bash[68] stdout `_ArgumentGroup` inherits from `_ActionsContainer` and is used to logically group a set of related arguments in help messages to improve readability. It does not directly handle argument parsing itself, but rather manages a specific set of argument actions as part of its parent container (`ArgumentParser` or another group).
