[log] bash[68] stdout - Global search: Search for keywords at any position in the path
[log] bash[68] stdout - Support for multiple keywords: Match multiple keywords simultaneously
[log] bash[68] stdout - Position weight: Matching at the end of the path and in directory names gets a higher weight
